To reproduce:
# Log into a Cloud instance (we used {{fuse-1551.jira-dev.com}}) as sysadmin
# Go to any project overview page, for example https://fuse-1551.jira-dev.com/browse/TEST
# The UI correctly reports a lack of permissions
# The JIRA log contains this NPE:

